    {"Pokemon Centers",
    "Vert Pokemon Center", "Bleu Pokemon Center", "Vernal Pokemon Center", "Magenta Pokemon Center", "Magenta Plaza Pokemon Center", "Rouge Pokemon Center", "Centrico Pokemon Center",
